  License:   MIT
  Copyright: Toru Nagashima and eslint-community contributors
  Pinned:    v4.7.2 (62a2c3a4ee30)
  Derived:   valid/invalid cases and oracle-materialized diagnostics converted from
             tests/lib/rules/*.js.

